name: Hand stitched Quilt
description:
Charming coordinating quilt and pilllow will catch your baby’s attention.
From naptime to tummy time, high contrast animal shapes will bring simple joy to your tiny one.

Soft and Warm 100% Cotton Voile Size: 36”x42”
Reverse side features red polka dots. Hand stitched.

We use non-toxic soy based inks.

name: Shaped Pillow
description:
Soft and warm sheep and rabbit pillows, the little pet of your tiny one!
100% Cotton voile, soy based printed and hand stitched.

name: Minitotes
description:
These charming little bags are the perfect size for kids or moms traveling light.
Throw in a snack or one diaper and wipes and hang from the stroller or let your toddler carry her own precious cargo inside.

 Size: 9” x 9”
100% Cotton Printed Canvas
Reverse side features polka dots

name: Wall art
description:
Baby’s eyes are drawn to high contrast patterns and images as they develop their vision.
Our Wall Art collection was created around this research on visual and brain development in the first year of a baby’s life. 
Our sweet animal designs will quickly become familiar friends as your baby begins to see his or her world.
Mix and Match: Choose from any of the animals to enliven baby’s room or anywhere children can enjoy them.
Size: 9x9" 
100% Cotton Canvas - Mounted on wood stretcher
